{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-002__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-002", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·002.1", "text_original": "四牡騑騑，周道倭遲。豈不懷歸？王事靡盬，我心傷悲。", "text_normalized": "四牡騑騑，周道倭遲。豈不懷歸？王事靡盬，我心傷悲。", "notes": "四牡 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-002", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·002.2", "text_original": "四牡騑騑，嘽嘽駱馬。豈不懷歸？王事靡盬，不遑啟處。", "text_normalized": "四牡騑騑，嘽嘽駱馬。豈不懷歸？王事靡盬，不遑啟處。", "notes": "四牡 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-002__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-002", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·002.3", "text_original": "翩翩者鵻，載飛載下，集于苞栩。王事靡盬，不遑將父。", "text_normalized": "翩翩者鵻，載飛載下，集于苞栩。王事靡盬，不遑將父。", "notes": "四牡 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-002__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-002", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·002.4", "text_original": "翩翩者鵻，載飛載止，集于苞杞。王事靡盬，不遑將母。", "text_normalized": "翩翩者鵻，載飛載止，集于苞杞。王事靡盬，不遑將母。", "notes": "四牡 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-002__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-002", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·002.5", "text_original": "駕彼四駱，載驟駸駸。豈不懷歸？是用作歌，將母來諗。", "text_normalized": "駕彼四駱，載驟駸駸。豈不懷歸？是用作歌，將母來諗。", "notes": "四牡 Chinese stanza 5."}
